
Basic requirements
==================

* QT 4.1 or greater.
* Alsalibs 1.0 or greater.

Building
========

1. Make sure you have QT and and alsa libraries, and their header files installed.
2. Make sure you have basic QT toolset (qmake, uic, moc) installed.
3. Type "qmake", which will build a Makefile for your platform.
4. Type "make".
5. Type "make install" to install the program to path.

All commands without quotes.


